name: Top O' the Mornin' Kendrick
description:
Top o' the mornin' fellow citizen. This is a meme to commemorate Baby Keem and Kendrick Lamar's iconic song "Range Brothers". This is also one of my 1st trials in learning animation using the Animation Paper app, which is really great check it out fellow animators!
